All keswanand student to remember this 
Yes or no

जो हम दूसरों को देंगे ,
वहीं लोटकर आएगा चाहे वो 
इज्ज़त हो समान हो या फिर धोखा।।।।।

There is plenty of people in life,
Someone's hand is enough on the shoulder
It does not matter whether it is too far or near
Just realization of true relationships is enough
